            "description": {
              "description": "A defensive unit that recovers HP every time she uses a skill."
            },
            "introduction": {
              "introduction": "　A defender who draws attention by performing area attacks.\n\n　It is a widely accepted theory that a Watch appears to those who develop a strong will to live before death, or to those with an equivalent tenacity. That explains how Hirose Aki could become a Counter. Her obsession towards living an idle life is unmatched.\n　Aki's ultimate goal is to find a stable source of income. The fastest way to make money would be to become a mercenary, but she has never even imagined herself working.\n　An experiment proved that Hirose Aki's greatsword changes weight based on the will of its master."
            },
